{
  "texts": [
    "For journals, we only retained journals with an impact factor of three or higher.",
    "For conferences, we only retained A-ranked conferences.",
    "In addition, to ensure that we did not discard any specialized venues regardless of their rank or impact factor, we retained any venue, whether journal or conference, with five or more publications.",
    "We conducted the quality-based intermediate screening to ensure that we focused on publications from top venues.",
    "This might have led to discarding some relevant papers, but we believe this step was crucial for quality assurance."
  ]
}